room_title: Escape room "Western" by Escape Out in Asheville
room_description: You and your team are looking into a corrupt local sheriff that owns a dodgy saloon in town as well. He owes you money so you burst into it one evening in the hopes of finding anything you may take to gather your loses. You have one hour at your disposal to gather valuables of any sort, anything left behind, before some of the sheriff’s boys come to ‘settle the matters” with you for good.
